title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Introducing the El Strickler Military Rifle
content:
Named after the notorious owner of Cayo Perico island, Juan Strickler, the El Strickler Military Rifle is just as fearsome as its namesake.

This unique weapon is pre-equipped with all the bells and whistles required for an iconic showdown, and available to claim for free one month early for GTA+ Members.

Visit the Gun Van to add one to your collection.
